WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: a7OeZBtYH9c

NOTE Language: en

00:34:08.900 --> 00:34:12.590
Today is a very important day.

00:34:25.200 --> 00:34:30.300
Hello. Better, is it?

00:34:34.600 --> 00:34:38.240
I’m saying today is very important.

00:34:43.460 --> 00:34:52.180
This is a new starting for you, for you all.

00:34:56.620 --> 00:35:05.290
Try to understand that you have worked
very hard so far

00:35:05.630 --> 00:35:10.840
and you wanted to do

00:35:13.140 --> 00:35:17.720
much more than you have been able to do.

00:35:18.770 --> 00:35:21.840
That was your desire

00:35:22.540 --> 00:35:29.590
and it will work out, definitely it will
work out.

00:35:30.070 --> 00:35:36.680
If your desire is strong, things will
work out

00:35:37.370 --> 00:35:43.840
and you’ll get a great chance of helping
people

00:35:45.460 --> 00:35:54.820
as you have helped yourself and you are
happy about it.

00:35:56.140 --> 00:36:00.390
It’s better that you decide to help others.

00:36:01.500 --> 00:36:08.500
It’s important, they all should be blessed.

00:36:12.570 --> 00:36:15.190
You can do it.

00:36:16.650 --> 00:36:20.530
There lies your leadership

00:36:21.790 --> 00:36:25.480
that you have to give it to others.

00:36:25.680 --> 00:36:32.240
Most of you have got it for yourself

00:36:34.620 --> 00:36:39.370
but you have to give it to others.

00:36:40.250 --> 00:36:47.450
Let the others also gain in their
spirituality.

00:36:55.870 --> 00:37:01.660
I know so many of you got your realisation

00:37:01.860 --> 00:37:08.800
and you are so much in it and you are
all very happy.

00:37:10.990 --> 00:37:14.220
So be happy and cheerful,

00:37:19.030 --> 00:37:22.000
that is the first sign

00:37:23.970 --> 00:37:29.800
that you are realised, you have got
the realisation.

00:37:32.760 --> 00:37:39.510
With this realisation you can give
realisation to others.

00:37:40.650 --> 00:37:48.560
The speciality of today is that Christ

00:37:50.800 --> 00:37:57.780
came back to life just to do something
for us.

00:38:03.560 --> 00:38:10.970
So it’s a very important day for all of us.

00:38:13.090 --> 00:38:20.750
I would say that today you should
understand that you have got this power

00:38:21.060 --> 00:38:27.110
to give realisation to others.

00:38:27.450 --> 00:38:33.300
You have got it but now you have to use.

00:38:33.500 --> 00:38:41.390
Those who have self realisation should
not waste their energy

00:38:41.590 --> 00:38:44.460
but try to give it.

00:38:45.530 --> 00:38:50.800
This world is full of chaos

00:38:51.000 --> 00:38:56.550
and quarrels and fighting still going on,

00:38:57.760 --> 00:39:05.880
so your duty and your job may be to talk
to them and tell them

00:39:06.080 --> 00:39:13.680
that first important is sahaja yogis must
become peaceful

00:39:13.880 --> 00:39:20.590
and they must enjoy the fruits of Sahaja
Yoga.

00:39:21.290 --> 00:39:28.590
I’m sure everything will work out. It has
worked out with so many of you

00:39:28.790 --> 00:39:32.860
and it will work out with others also.

00:39:35.090 --> 00:39:40.560
It’s not just a talk but there’s something
happening,

00:39:40.760 --> 00:39:46.920
so try to remember that you are all sahaja
yogis

00:39:47.120 --> 00:39:56.480
and you deserve a very good help,

00:40:01.590 --> 00:40:11.350
very good help from Me and from God
Almighty.

00:40:11.570 --> 00:40:18.240
There is nothing to be upset,

00:40:20.820 --> 00:40:25.820
these are all different tests,

00:40:28.580 --> 00:40:35.370
which will work out the goodness in you

00:40:36.030 --> 00:40:40.120
and will get the results.

00:40:40.330 --> 00:40:48.030
You’ll find sahaja yogis, special ones.

00:40:50.350 --> 00:40:54.180
It’s very nice to see so many of you

00:40:57.090 --> 00:41:02.060
who have tried to get realisation,

00:41:02.580 --> 00:41:07.030
but who are really already realised,

00:41:07.230 --> 00:41:11.250
there are many who want to have
realisation.

00:41:11.460 --> 00:41:17.460
But there are already many who are already
realised

00:41:17.660 --> 00:41:25.010
and who can do a lot for others who want
their help.

00:41:26.050 --> 00:41:32.230
Today is a good day for you have to decide
for your future.

00:41:33.330 --> 00:41:37.060
You have to decide that you are to do

00:41:39.340 --> 00:41:44.200
to help other sahaja yogis

00:41:44.700 --> 00:41:49.160
to get more sahaja yogis.

00:41:49.440 --> 00:41:52.890
We have to spread Sahaja Yoga.

00:41:53.480 --> 00:41:57.220
You see so many problems are there

00:41:58.310 --> 00:42:02.830
and the more we have as sahaja yogis,

00:42:03.530 --> 00:42:10.400
there’s no problem left, it will be all
solved.

00:42:10.600 --> 00:42:13.150
So I wish you luck

00:42:13.350 --> 00:42:19.730
that please try to get your realisation

00:42:19.930 --> 00:42:24.680
proper and confirmed.

00:42:27.060 --> 00:42:32.120
I hope you don’t have doubts about it.

00:42:34.830 --> 00:42:40.290
If you have any doubts, you can write to me.

00:42:53.110 --> 00:43:00.510
Now we have got some very nice good
people who have come to Sahaja Yoga,

00:43:01.470 --> 00:43:06.380
so it is your duty to see that they become
good sahaja yogis

00:43:06.580 --> 00:43:11.980
and enjoy the blessings.

00:43:16.170 --> 00:43:21.080
I’m very happy to see so many of you coming

00:43:21.280 --> 00:43:26.240
and today being a very good day also.

00:43:30.160 --> 00:43:37.190
In the life of Christ very great thing
happened

00:43:37.390 --> 00:43:40.400
that He became,

00:43:44.920 --> 00:43:50.710
He became what He was already, a sahaja
yogi

00:43:50.910 --> 00:43:56.470
and He tried to make many sahaja yogis
if possible.

00:43:56.890 --> 00:44:03.840
But at that time the people were not so
alert as you are.

00:44:04.050 --> 00:44:09.800
You are special people who are seeking

00:44:12.430 --> 00:44:18.690
and who have found out and you can give it
to others.

00:44:18.890 --> 00:44:25.810
This is not for keeping with yourself.
If you have got it,

00:44:26.010 --> 00:44:33.640
just don’t think that you have got the last
chance

00:44:33.840 --> 00:44:36.990
but give chance to others.

00:44:39.790 --> 00:44:42.190
I’m all with you.

00:44:42.390 --> 00:44:50.670
Any one of you has any personal or any
other problem you should write to me.

00:44:51.530 --> 00:44:57.320
I’m sorry I won’t be able to

00:44:58.610 --> 00:45:04.520
give anything for this special day.

00:45:40.580 --> 00:45:43.810
May God bless you all.
